{"tid":1009042,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"年三十賣懶吃紅雞蛋　初一禁洗頭沖涼","createTime":"2019-02-05T02:15:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-05T08:17:13.000Z","uid":81228,"like":3,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"a9ef6055edeeb6802514297cda2a190fa6751497","tid":1009042,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T02:15:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190204/s00001/2085647893ce0ab574ed1330ee49378f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190204%2Fs00001%2F2085647893ce0ab574ed1330ee49378f.jpg&h=4460fc40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n廣東年三十有賣懶習俗。（中通社／明報製圖）<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190204/s00001/208567559433bd00df9aabae00e910bb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190204%2Fs00001%2F208567559433bd00df9aabae00e910bb.jpg&h=e0b8263d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n嶺南大學中文系講師蕭欣浩博士（資料圖片）<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190204/s00001/20856ae8f6c7069f75aceb2583723898.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190204%2Fs00001%2F20856ae8f6c7069f75aceb2583723898.jpg&h=7df3ced5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n蕭欣浩博士表示，年三十拿着紅雞蛋，上香後把它吃掉，就完成賣懶。（陳翠美攝）<br />\n<br />\n過新年穿新衣，年三十吃團年飯！傳統過農曆新年，年三十晚、新正頭都有不少禁忌，經常聽到「賣懶，賣懶，賣到年三十晚！」嶺南大學中文系講師蕭欣浩博士趁今日（4日）是年三十，解釋賣懶的意思。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>年三十 年夜飯、賣懶、壓歲錢</strong><br />\n<br />\n年三十食團年飯、在枕頭下放壓歲錢。賣懶究竟是什麼？賣懶是廣東的過年習俗，年三十拿着紅雞蛋，上香後把它吃掉，就完成賣懶，這風俗寓意在新年可以戒掉懶惰，變得勤奮。需注意的是，人們在年三十入夜前便要洗澡，並把衣服洗晾完成，不能濕著過年。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>年初一 穿新衣、說好話、做好事</strong><br />\n<br />\n大年初一，大人小孩都要開開心心，穿新衣新鞋、說好話、做好事，為新一年討個好兆頭。這天不能洗澡、洗頭、洗衣物、打掃和倒垃圾，因為「洗」和「死」的諧音相近，不吉利，這樣也會把財運洗掉。<br />\n<br />\n另外，初一小心不可打破東西！若打破便要用紅紙包起來，放置在神桌上默念「歲歲平安」的吉祥話語，靜待五日後再丟棄。出嫁女兒亦不能在初一、初四、初五回娘家。<br />\n<br />\n資料提供：嶺南大學中文系講師蕭欣浩博士<br />\n編輯：陳翠美 cmchan@mingpao.com<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190204/s00001/1549249281339/%E3%80%90%E8%B1%AC%E5%B9%B4%E5%88%B0-%E8%BE%B2%E6%9B%86%E6%96%B0%E5%B9%B4%E7%BF%92%E4%BF%972%E3%80%91%E5%B9%B4%E4%B8%89%E5%8D%81%E8%B3%A3%E6%87%B6%E5%90%83%E7%B4%85%E9%9B%9E%E8%9B%8B-%E5%88%9D%E4%B8%80%E7%A6%81%E6%B4%97%E9%A0%AD%E6%B2%96%E6%B6%BC\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190204%2Fs00001%2F1549249281339%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E8%25B1%25AC%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%2588%25B0-%25E8%25BE%25B2%25E6%259B%2586%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E7%25BF%2592%25E4%25BF%25972%25E3%2580%2591%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E4%25B8%2589%25E5%258D%2581%25E8%25B3%25A3%25E6%2587%25B6%25E5%2590%2583%25E7%25B4%2585%25E9%259B%259E%25E8%259B%258B-%25E5%2588%259D%25E4%25B8%2580%25E7%25A6%2581%25E6%25B4%2597%25E9%25A0%25AD%25E6%25B2%2596%25E6%25B6%25BC&d=Hj%2FeMeEVpmzVIwD%2FtvFBFseYC5A6rl8%2B6t9FBevN87M%3D&h=5872d6ba\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190204%2Fs00001%2F1549249281339%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E8%25B1%25AC%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%2588%25B0-%25E8%25BE%25B2%25E6%259B%2586%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E7%25BF%2592%25E4%25BF%25972%25E3%2580%2591%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E4%25B8%2589%25E5%258D%2581%25E8%25B3%25A3%25E6%2587%25B6%25E5%2590%2583%25E7%25B4%2585%25E9%259B%259E%25E8%259B%258B-%25E5%2588%259D%25E4%25B8%2580%25E7%25A6%2581%25E6%25B4%2597%25E9%25A0%25AD%25E6%25B2%2596%25E6%25B6%25BC&h=3c457983\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190204/s00001/1549249281339/%E3%80%90%E8%B1%AC%E5%B9%B4%E5%88%B0-%E8%BE%B2%E6%9B%86%E6%96%B0%E5%B9%B4%E7%BF%92%E4%BF%972%E3%80%91%E5%B9%B4%E4%B8%89%E5%8D%81%E8%B3%A3%E6%87%B6%E5%90%83%E7%B4%85%E9%9B%9E%E8%9B%8B-%E5%88%9D%E4%B8%80%E7%A6%81%E6%B4%97%E9%A0%AD%E6%B2%96%E6%B6%BC</a>"},{"pid":"a7c0335e34b0042e3489520771854556cc2e9f12","tid":1009042,"uid":10788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T07:35:33.000Z","msg":"..."},{"pid":"e220c21104291e4206d480d